{
  "chapter": 70,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙返回府邸后，就赵致之事严厉质问荆俊。荆俊承认已向赵致泄露行踪，但声称赵致与赵穆有深仇且只爱项少龙。滕翼和乌卓主张杀赵致灭口，项少龙认为会引人怀疑，乌卓建议将赵致变为项少龙的女人以控制她。荆俊为成全赵致甘愿放弃感情。正商议间，精兵团大头领乌果报告有神秘来客，竟是纪嫣然女扮男装前来。项少龙与纪嫣然互诉衷肠，共度春宵，感情彻底确立。纪嫣然表示从未对李园动心，深爱项少龙的胸襟气魄与英雄气概。天亮前项少龙护送纪嫣然回到刘华生府，心中充满甜蜜温馨。本章为第二册终章。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "小俊！你究竟向赵致透露过什么？不准有任何隐瞒。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三哥见到赵致了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你这无知小子，不分轻重，你是否想所有人为你的愚蠢行为丧命，我们早警告过你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "那警告来得太迟了，我早告诉她我们会在短期内回来。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你难道不知赵致是赵人吗？若她爱赵国的心多过爱你，会是怎样的后果。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "她根本不爱我，爱的只是三哥。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你莫要胡言乱语，图开脱自己的责任。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "是她亲口告诉你的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "她仅当我是个淘气爱玩的小弟弟，肯和我说话，只是想多知道点三哥的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "她最后给你那封信说什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她问我何时来邯郸，要不要接应。唉！我也不是没有想过她是赵人的问题，而是她告诉我与赵穆有深仇，所以我才相信她不会出卖我们。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "她和赵穆有什么冤仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "她不肯说出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说不定是和女儿家的贞操有关。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赵致的家族有什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "她好像只是与她爹相依为命，我……我什么都不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你真是糊涂误事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "你不是回信给她吗？信里说什么呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "我告诉她我们将会以伪装身份在邯郸出现，到达后找机会与她联络。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "情势尚未太坏，她虽似认出是我，一来还不大肯定，二来没有揭破我，可知仍有转圜的余地。不过我真不明白，若你明知她只当你是小弟弟，为何仍要与她纠缠不清？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我都不明白，不过假若她成了你的女人，小俊绝不会有丝毫不满。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "我们不能让命运操纵在一个女人手里，小俊你给我带路，我要亲手杀掉她，以免夜长梦多。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来这是唯一的办法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "这样做会未见其利，先见其害，赵致今晚曾多次与我说话，又对我特别注意，这情况会落到一些有心人眼里。假若她这么见我一面后，当晚立即被杀，终有人会猜到我头上来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那另一方法是把她变成你的女人，使我们可绝对的控制她，同时可查清她的底细。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "小俊是我的好兄弟，我怎能夺他所爱？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有三哥这么一句话，小俊已深切感受到兄弟之情，事实上三哥早让小俊享尽人间荣华富贵，小俊尚未有报答的机会。今天又是小俊犯错，差点累死所有人。三哥请放手处置赵致，小俊只有心服口服。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "我对赵致虽有好感，却从没有想到男女方面的关系去，脑筋一时很难转过来，何况更有点像要去夺取自己好兄弟的女人似的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事谁都知少龙是为所有人的生命安危去做，不须有任何顾忌，若因小俊而误了大局，滕翼万死不能辞其咎。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "就这么办，事不宜迟，不若少龙立即去找赵致，问个清楚明白，若有问题，狠心点也没得说了，总好过坐以待毙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三哥！我立即带你去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "我联络上纪嫣然了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有位不肯表露身份的客人来找姑爷，现在客厅里等候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去看看！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "想不到嫣然今晚就来找我，项少龙受宠若惊了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然一刻都等不下去，这大半年来人家每天均度日如年，饱受思念你的折磨，若非可与邹先生不时谈起你，人家更受不了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_guo",
      "text": "告诉他们是谁来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "嫣然！项少龙很感激你的垂青，你对我太好哩！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "这样好吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "老天爷多么不公平，嫣然早看过我的身体，我却要苦候大半年才有此扳平的机会。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家只是为你疗伤，最羞人的部分都是由你的倩公主一手包办，哪有像你眼前般对待人家啊！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "纪才女终于回复说话的能力了呀！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你只懂调笑人家。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "我的天啊！这真是老天爷令人感动的杰作。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎啊！天亮前人家还要赶回去呀！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "那还不转过身来？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "快乐吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "想不到男女间竟有这么动人的滋味，嫣然似感到以前都是白活了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是否怕人家喜欢上李园呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你太小觑嫣然了，美男子我不知见过多少，除你外没有人能令嫣然有半丝心动。项少龙所以能打动纪嫣然，亦不全因他长得比别人好看，而是因他的胸襟气魄、超凡的智慧和一种令人无法抗拒的英雄气概。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在还加上床笫的缠绵恩爱、男女之乐。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 70,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    }
  ],
